{
  "text": "To construct dyon solutions numerically, we employ the static axially symmetric ansatz used in the numerical construction of multimonopoles [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , supplemented by a nonvanishing time-component of the gauge field. In spherical coordinates with A",
